query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('analytic-number-theory',
'ca.classical-analysis-and-odes',
'graph-theory',
'homotopy-theory',
'lie-groups',
'matrices',
'ra.rings-and-algebras',
'real-analysis',
'riemannian-geometry');
